CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 1, 1945, pg. 13, reads: "'Way Up There! - They're Aniketos, at Clairton swimming pool... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: William Battles, Rosemarie Lawrence (Cook), Mozelle Thompson, Lois Weaver Watson, Don Matheus, Jimmy Bertha, and Frank Entry standing on steps at swimming pool in Clairton
